<p><b><font style="font-size: 12px;" class="text-delta">Business Development Manager</font></b></p>
<p><font style="font-size: 12px;" class="text-black">Mobile/Whatsapp: ${object.user_id.partner_id.mobiile}</font></p>
<p><font style="font-size: 12px;" class="text-black">E-mail: <a href="mailto:${object.user_id.partner_id.email}" target="_blank"></a></font></p>
<p><font style="font-size: 12px;" class="text-black">Website:&nbsp;</font><a href="http://zimmer-rattan.com/" data-original-title="" title="">www.zimmer-rattan.com</a></p>
<hr>
<p><b>ZIMMER RATTAN INDONESIA</b></p>
<p>${company.rml_header1}</p>
<p>${company.street}</p><p>${company.street2}, ${company.city}, ${company.state_id.name}, ${company.zip}</p>
<p>tel: ${company.phone}</p>
<p>fax: ${company.fax}</p>
<p>sms/wa info center: ${company.partner_id.mobile}</p>
<p>e-mail info center:&nbsp;<a href="mailto:sales@zimmer-rattan.com">sales@zimmer-rattan.com</a></p>
<p><a href="mailto:sales@zimmer-rattan.com"><br></a><b>ZIMMER RATTAN INDONESIA</b></p><p>Since 2011 becoming Partner of 2,800 Projects, Trusted by 5<span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: initial; font-variant-ligatures: initial; font-variant-caps: initial; font-weight: initial;">â˜… Hotels, Apartments, Luxury Houses and Villas.</span><br><br></p>
<p><a href="http://zimmer-rattan.com/"><font class="text-black">Zimmer-Rattan.com</font></a>&nbsp;is Indonesia's <font class="text-gamma"><b>Leading Manufacturer</b> </font><font class="text-black">for</font><font class="text-gamma"> <b>Outdoor Furniture</b> </font><font class="text-black">and </font><font class="text-gamma"><b>Pioneer of Zimmer Smart Warranty</b> </font><font class="text-black">that is capable giving </font><font class="text-gamma"><b>10-YEAR Warranty</b></font><font class="text-black">, founded by CEO Evan Hiumawan, B.Sc., achieved global exporting to more than 12 countries at the age of 19.</font><br></p>
]]></field>
        </record>

        <record id="project_proforma_invoice" model="project.project">
            <field name="sequence">10</field>
            <field name="name">Pro-forma Invoice</field>
            <field name="label_tasks">Tasks</field>
            <field name="alias_model">project.task</field>
            <field name="type_ids" eval="[(4, ref('project.project_stage_0')), (4, ref('project.project_stage_1')), (4, ref('project.project_stage_2')),]"/>
            <field name="privacy_visibility">employees</field>
        </record>
    </data>
</odoo>